## Fix 1 — Correct the download path (space in folder name)

Use quotes around the full output path:

```cmd
curl -k -o "D:\Mr Om\Python_script\python-installer.exe" "https://artifactory.jfrog.sbi:443/artifactory/itepaypg-sbiepay2-python-virtual/packages/python-3.11.9-amd64.exe"
```

---

## Fix 2 — JFrog needs your credentials

Use your SBI LDAP credentials with curl `-u` flag:

```cmd
curl -k -u "v1021577:YOUR_PASSWORD" -o "D:\Mr Om\Python_script\python-installer.exe" "https://artifactory.jfrog.sbi:443/artifactory/itepaypg-sbiepay2-python-virtual/packages/python-3.11.9-amd64.exe"
```

Replace `YOUR_PASSWORD` with your actual Windows/LDAP password.

